WRATIO.description:
Ratio of maximum landing weight to maximum takeoff
weight (Default = WLDG/GW if WLDG is input, otherwise
for supersonic aircraft Default = 1. - .00009*DESRNG,
for subsonic aircraft Default = 1. - .00004*DESRNG)

HSTOP.description:
Segment termination altitude, ft
(Default = value from following segment or OBSTO
from Namelist $TOLIN for the 'OBSTACLE' segment)
